<HEADLINE>
<P>
BOB HOPE'S 7,400 ACRES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Walter Annenberg donates $50 million to the United Negro College Fund. Bob Hope 
wants to make $50 million on 7,400 acres of mountain terrain that could be 
donated for desperately needed parkland. What a difference in values! One 
leaves a legacy for the future; the other leaves a legacy of greed. 
</P>
<P>
FRANK M. STRICKLIN 
</P>
<P>
Chatsworth 
</P>
</TEXT>
