</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Former Clemson running back Terry Allen faces at least 10 days in jail for 
driving with a license suspended last fall when he pleaded guilty to driving 
under the influence, authorities in Clemson, S.C., said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
