from Neiman Marcus. MARSHA TRAEGER / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Massive gold 
earrings, $85, and large gold swirl brooch, $70, both available from I. Magnin. 
JIM MENDENHALL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
