POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; KOHL, HELMUT; BRANDT, WILLY; EAST GERMANY -- CURRENCY; 
WEST GERMANY -- CURRENCY; EAST GERMANY -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY; 
REUNIFICATION 
</P>
