<TEXT>
<P>
WATER SPORT: First BMWs, then hotel boxing matches and now it's . . . 
underwater vacations: Orange County scuba shops (C15) report a business boom as 
a result of young professionals taking scuba diving courses. But few are 
setting a webbed foot in California waters. . . . "I do not cold-water dive," 
