<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Computer Automation Names President: Computer Automation Inc. of Irvine named 
William L. Osmundsen, the firm's chief financial officer, to the additional 
titles of president, chief operating officer and director. 
</P>
<P>
Osmundsen replaces Douglas L. Cutsforth, who resigned last April. He said the 
company, which has been trying to sell its automatic test equipment business, 
is "nearing an acceptable resolution" for disposition of the operation. He did 
not elaborate. Computer Automation also makes data communications equipment, 
heavy-duty microcomputers and facsimile subsystems. 
</P>
